hadiths[140]{hadithnumber,text}:
1416,"Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Quran walo ! witr padha karo . bila-shuba Shan Wala Allah witr ( akela ( hai, witr ko pasand karta hai.''"
1417,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se uskey ham-maani riwayat ki hai aur mazeed ye izafa kiya hai ke eik dehati bola , aap kya kehtey hain? (Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : ye hukm tumhen aur tumharey sathiyon ke liye nahin hai."
1418,Khaarija bin Huzafa Adwi (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : ''bila-shuba Allah taala ne eik (mazeed izafi) Namaz se tumhari madad farmaee hai aur ye tumharey liye surkh oonton se bhi badh kar hai. ye Namaz witr hai aur iska waqt Isha se tulu Fajr ke darmiyan muqarrar farmaya hai.''
1419,"Abdullah bin Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unka bayan hai ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : ''witr haq hai, jo witr na padhey wo ham mein se nahin. witr haq hai, jo witr na padhey wo ham mein se nahin. witr haq hai, jo witr na padhey wo ham mein se nahin.''"
1420,"Ibne Muhaireez se marwi (bayan) hai ke bano kinaana ke eik shakhs Makhdazi naami ne shaam main eik shakhs ko suna jisey Abu-Muhammad kaha jata tha, wo kehta tha ke witr wajib hai. Makhdazi ne kaha ke main Hazrat Ubada bin Saamit (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya aur unhen Abu-Muhammad ki baat batai. to Hazrat Ubada ne kaha : Abu-Muhammad ne ghalat kaha. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna hai, aap farmatey they : ''paanch namaazen hain jo Allah ne bandon par farz ki hain. jisney unhen ada kya aur unka haq halka samajhtey huey un mein se kuchh zaya na kiya to aisey shakhs ke liye Allah ke zimmey ye ehad hai ke wo usey jannat mein dakhil kerega. aur jisney unko ada na kiya to aisey shakhs ke liye Allah ke yahan koi ehad nahin, chahey to usey azab dey aur chahey to jannat mein dakhil kar dey.''"
1421,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik dehati aadmi ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se raat ki Namaz ke baarey mein puchha to aapney apni ungliyon se ishara kartey huey farmaya : ''is tarah, do do rakaat. aur witr eik rakat hai raat ke aakhir mein.''"
1422,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''witr Namaz her musalman par haq hai, chunanche jo paanch padhna chahey , padh ley . aur jo teen padhna chahey , padh ley . aur jo eik padhna chahey , wo eik padh ley.''"
1423,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaze-witr mein {( سَبِّحِ اسْمَ رَبِّكَ الْأَعْلَى ( , ( قل ياأيها الكافرون (aur ( قل ھوَاللَّهُ َاحِدُ )} padha kartey they."
1424,Abdul-Azeez bin Juraij kehtey hain ke maine Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) witron mein kya padha kartey they? to mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya aur kaha : ''teesri rakaat mein) قل هو الله أحد (aur ''muawwizatain'' ( Sura Falaq aur Sura Naas ( padha kartey they.''
1425,"Abu-Is'haaq ne bareed bin abi Maryam se unhoney Abul Hora se riwayat ki ke Janab Hasan bin Ali (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey kuch kalimaat taaleem farmaee jinhen main witr mein kaha karun. ( ustaad ( ibne Jawas ke lafz hain : ''main inhen witr ke qunoot mein padha karun.'' aur wo ye hain : ( اللَّهُمَّ ! اهْدِنِي فِيمَنْ هَدَيْتَ , وَعَافِنِي فِيمَنْ عَافَيْتَ , وَتَوَلَّنِي فِيمَنْ تَوَلَّيْتَ , وَبَارِكْ لِي فِيمَا أَعْطَيْتَ , وَقِنِي شَرَّمَا قَضَيْتَ , إِنَّكَ تَقْضِي وَلَا يُقْضَى عَلَيْكَ , وَإِنَّهُ لَا يَذِلُّ مَنْ وَالَيْتَ وَلَا يَعِزُّ مَنْ عَادَيْتَ , تَبَارَكْتَ رَبَّنَا وَتَعَالَيْتَ ) ''aey Allah ! jin logon ko to ne hidayat di hai mujhey bhi unke sath hidayat dey . aur jin ko to ne aafiyat di hai mujhey bhi unke sath aafiyat dey (yani her qisam ki buraiyon aur pareshaniyon waghaira se). aur jin ka to wali) dost aur muhafiz ( bana hai unke sath mera bhi wali bin . aur jo nematen to ne inayat farmaee hain un mein mujhey barkat dey . aur jo faisley to ne farmaai hain unke shar se mujhey mehfooz rakh . bila-shuba faisley to hi karta hai, terey muqabley mein koi faisla nahin hota . aur jiska to wali aur muhafiz ho wo kahin zaleel nahin ho sakta. aur jiska to mukhalif ho wo kabhi izzat nahin pa sakta , badi barkaton (aur azmaton ( wala hai to aey hamarey Rab ! aur bahut buland aur baala hai.''"
1426,Abu-Is'haaq ne apni sanad se mazkura hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya. us riwayat ke aakhir mein hai ke usey witr ke qunoot mein kahey aur ye jumla nahin kaha ke main unhen witr mein kahun. Abul Hora ka naam Rabeea bin Sheban hai.
1427,"Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney witr ke aakhir mein ye kaha kartey they : (اللَّهُمَّ ! إِنِّي أَعُوذُ بِرِضَاكَ مِنْ سُخْطِكَ وَ بِمُعَا فَاتِكَ مِنْ عُقُوبَتِكَ , وَأَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْكَ لَا أُحْصِي ثَنَاءً عَلَيْكَ أَنْتَ كَمَا أَثْنَيْتَ عَلَى نَفْسِكَ ) ''aey Allah ! main teri narazi se bachtey huey teri raza ki panah mein aata hun. terey muwaakhizey (pakad) se bachtey huey teri mafi aur karam ki panah leta hun. main tujh se (yani terey ghusse aur ghazab sey) teri (rehmat ki) aman chahta hun. main teri tareefen shumar nahin kar sakta. to waisa hi hai jaisey ke to ne khud apni sifaat bayan farmae hai.'' Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Hisham , Hammad ke qadim tareen ustad hain. aur Yahya bin Moayan se marwi (bayan) hai ke un ( Hisham ( se siwaye Hammad bin Salma ke aur kisi ne riwayat nahin ki. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Esa bin Yunus ne Saeed bin Abi Aruba sey, unhoney Qatada sey, unhoney Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abza sey, unhoney apney walid sey, unhoney Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne rukoo se pehley qunoot padhi. yani witr mein. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Esa bin Yunus ne ye hadees bhi Fitr bin Khalifa sey, unhoney Zubeda sey, unhoney Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abza sey, wo apney walid sey, wo Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala ke jaisi riwayat ki hai. aur Hafs bin Ghiyas se marwi (bayan) hai, wo Musaair se wo Zubeda sey, wo Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abza sey, wo apney walid sey, wo Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne witr mein rukoo se pehley qunoot padhi. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Saeed bin Abi Aruba ki (mazkura baala) riwayat jo unhoney Qatada se riwayat ki hai usko Yazid bin Zareea' ne Saeed sey, unhoney Qatada sey, unhoney Azra sey, unhoney Saeed bin Abdur-Rehman bin Abza sey, unhoney apney walid sey, unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat ki hai, magar is mein qunoot ka zikr kiya na Ubai bin Kab ka. yani mursal hai. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke isko Abdul-A'alaa aur Muhammad bin Bishr Abdi ne bhi aisey hi riwayat kiya hai. aur un ( Muhammad bin Bishr (ka samaa, Esa bin Yunus ke sath koofa mein Sabit hai. unhoney qunoot ka zikr nahin kiya hai. aur isko Hisham Dustwaai aur Shoba ne bhi Qatada se riwayat kiya hai aur in dono ne qunoot ka zikr nahin kiya.  Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : aur hadees Zubeda ko Sulaiman Aamash , Shoba Abdul-Malik bin abi Sulaiman aur Jarir bin Hazim sabhi ne Zubeda se riwayat kiya hai, magar in mein se kisi ne bhi qunoot ka zikr nahin kiya siwaye Hafs bin Ghiyas ke jisey unhoney b-waasta Musaair , Zubeda se riwayat kiya hai ke ''aapney rukoo se pehley qunoot padhi.''  Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Hafs ki ye hadees mashhoor nahin hai, andesha hai ke Musaair ke Alawa kisi aur se riwayat hogi . Abu-Dawud kehtey hain : riwayat hai ke Hazrat Abi (Raziallahu anhu) nisf Ramazan mein qunoot padha kartey they."
1428,Muhammad bin Sirin apney baaz sathiyon se riwayat kartey hain ke Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne unki Ramazan mein imaamat karaai aur wo Ramazan ke nisf aakhir mein qunoot padha kartey they.
1429,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon ko Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) par jama farma diya. wo unhen bees raat Namaz padhatey they aur qunoot na kartey they, magar nisf akheer mein qunoot kartey they. aur jab aakhiri ashra aa jata to jamaat karana chhod detey aur apney ghar mein padhtey they to log kehtey ke Ubai bhag gaey. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain : ye daleel hai ke qunoot ke baarey mein jo zikr hua wo sahih nahin hai. aur ye dono hadeesen Hazrat Ubai se marwi (bayan) is hadees ke zaeef honey ki daleel hain jis mein hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) witr mein qunoot padha kartey they."
1430,Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab witr se salam phertey to kehtey :(سُبْحَانَ الْمَلِكِ الْقُدُّوسِ ) ''paak hai wo zaat jo haakim mutlab hai aur har lihaz se paak hai.''
1431,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney witr padhney se so jaey (aur na padh sakey (ya bhool jaey to jab yaad aaye padh ley.''
1432,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke merey khaleel (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey teen baaton ki wasiyat farmae thi , main unhen safar aur hazar mein nahin chhodta , chaasht ki do rakaten , her mahiney mein teen rozey aur ye ke witr padhey baghair na soun."
1433,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke merey khaleel (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey teen baaton ki wasiyat farmae thi , main unhen kisi soorat nahin chhodta . mujhey wasiyat farmae ke her mahiney teen din ke rozey rakhun , witr padh kar soyaa karun aur zuha ke nafl padhun safar aur hazar mein."
1434,Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : ''tum witr kis waqt padhtey ho? '' unhoney kaha : main raat ke awwal hissey mein padhta hun. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke tum witr kis waqt padhtey ho? unhoney kaha : main raat ke aakhiri hissey mein padhta hun. aapney Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutalliq farmaya : ''usney ehtiyat ko ikhtiyar kiya hai.'' aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke baarey mein farmaya : ''usney azm w quwwat ko ikhtiyar kiya hai.''
1435,"Masruq bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kis waqt witr padha kartey they? unhoney kaha : aapney sab hi auqaat (waqton) mein witr padhey hain. raat ke shuru mein , darmiyan mein aur aakhir mein bhi . lekin aakhiri zindagi mein aap ke witr sahar ke waqt honey lagey they."
1436,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''subah honey se pehley pehley witr padh lo.''
1437,"Janab Abdullah bin Ubai Qais bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke witron ke mutalliq puchha , to unhoney kaha : kabhi to aap raat ke pehley hissey mein padh letey they aur kabhi raat ke aakhir mein . maine aap ki qirat ke baarey mein puchha ke kya aap khamoshi se padhtey they ya buland aawaz se ? unhoney kaha : aap her tarah kar letey they, kabhi khamoshi se padhtey aur kabhi buland aawaz se. aur kabhi ghusl karkey so jatey aur kabhi wuzu karkey so rehtey . Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha, Quteba ke alawa doosrey raawiyon ne kaha ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka ishara ghusle-janabat ki taraf tha."
1438,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni raat ki aakhiri Namaz witr ko banao.''
1439,"Qais bin Talaq bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Talaq bin Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Ramazan main eik din hamare yahan aaye aur hamarey hi yahaan shaam ki aur iftaar kiya, aur phir hamein us raat Namaz padhaai aur witr bhi padhaaey, phir apni masjid ki taraf chaley gaey aur wahan apney sathiyon ko Namaz padhaai. aur jab witr baqi rahey to eik shakhs ko aagey kar diya aur kaha : apney sathiyon ko witr padhao, be-shak maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they. ''eik raat mein do witr nahin.'' (yani do baar witr nahin.)"
1440,"Janab Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman kehtey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : qasam Allah ki ! main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki si Namaz padhaaun ga . chunanche wo namaze-Zohar , Isha aur Fajr ki aakhiri rakaat mein qunoot padhtey they, momineen ke liye dua kartey aur kuffar par lanat."
1441,Hazrat Bara (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) subah ki Namaz mein qunoot padha kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke ibne Muaz ne mazeed kaha ke Namaze-Maghrib mein bhi.
1442,"Janab Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman kehtey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Isha ki Namaz main eik mahiney tak qunoot padhi. aap apney qunoot mein ye dua kartey they : ''aey Allah ! Waleed bin Waleed ko najat dey . aey Allah ! Salma bin Hisham ko najat dey. aey Allah zaeef momineen ko najat dey . aey Allah ! qabeela Muzar par apni saza sakht kar dey . aey Allah ! un par qehat musallat kar dey jaisa ke qaume Yusuf par aaya tha.''  Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke eik din aapney dua na ki to maine aap se puchha , to aapney farmaya : ''kya dekhtey nahin ke wo aa gey hain.''"
1443,"Janab Ikrima se Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka ye bayan manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik mahina mutawatir (lagataar) zohar, asr, maghrib, Isha aur Fajr ki namazon mein qunoot padhi. har Namaz ki aakhiri rakaat mein rukoo sey, (سمع الله لمن حمده) kehney ke baad. bano sulaim mein se Ri'al, Zakwaan aur Usba ke qabaayel par bad-dua kartey they aur aap ke peechhey waley aameen kehtey they."
1444,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha gaya : kya Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne namaze-Fajr mein qunoot padhi thi ? unhoney kaha : haan . puchha gaya : rukoo se pehley ya baad ? kaha : rukoo ke baad. Musaddad ki riwayat mein hai ke . ... . thodi muddat tak.
1445,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik mahiney tak qunoot padhi , phir chhod di."
1446,Janab Muhammad bin Sirin kehtey hain mujhey us shakhs ne bayan kiya jisney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Fajr ki Namaz padhi thi ke jab aapney dusri rakaat se sar uthaya to thodi der khadey rahey. (qunoot ke liye)
1447,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne masjid mein hujra bana liya , aap raat ko ghar se tashrif latey aur us hujrey mein Namaz padhtey . kaha ke logon ne bhi aap ki Namaz ke sath Namaz padhi aur wo her raat aap ke paas aatey , yahan tak ke eik raat aap tashrif na laye to wo khaansney lagey. (taake aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko tanbeeh ho.) kuch ne apni aawazen buland kin aur (kuch ne) aap ke darwazey par kankariyaan bhi maarin. bil-aakhir aap tashrif laye to ghussay mein they aur farmaya : ''logo ! tumhara barabar yehi haal raha , yahan tak ke mujhey andesha hua ke tum par farz na kar di jaey. so apney gharon mein Namaz padho. bila-shuba farz ke alawa mard ki behtareen Namaz wohi hai jo wo apney ghar mein padhey.''"
1448,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni namazon ka kuch hissey gharon mein bhi padha karo aur unhen qabristaan mat bana dalo.''
1449,Hazrat Abdullah bin Habshi Al Khas'ami  (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya : kaun sa amal afzal hai? aapney farmaya : ''lamba qiyam.'' kaha gaya : kaun sa sadqa afzal hai? farmaya : ''jo qaleel (thoda) maal wala mehnat karkey sadqa dey.'' kaha gaya : kaun si hijrat afzal hai? farmaya : ''jo shakhs Allah ke haram karda umur (baton) ko chhod dey.'' kaha gaya : kaun sa jihad afzal hai? farmaya : ''jo shakhs mushrekin se apney maal aur apni jaan ke sath jihad karey.'' puchha gaya : kaun sa qatl sharf wala hai? aapney farmaya : ''jis ka khoon baha diya gaya aur uskey ghodey ko bhi kaat diya gaya.''
1450,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''reham karey Allah us shakhs par jo raat ko uth kar Namaz padhta aur apni biwi ko jagata hai aur wo bhi Namaz padhti hai. agar inkar karti hai, to uskey chehrey par pani ke chheentey maarta hai. aur rehem karey Allah taala us aurat par jo raat ko uthti aur Namaz padhti hai aur apney shohar ko bhi jagaati hai. aur agar wo inkar karta hai, to uskey chehrey par pani ke chheentey maarti hai.''"
1451,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri aur Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs raat ko jaagey aur apni biwi ko bhi jagaaey , phir wo dono do rakaten padhen to unka shumar zaakreen aur zaakiraat mein hota hai jo Allah ko bahut ziyada yaad kerney waley hotey hain.''"
1452,Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein sab se behtar wo shakhs hai jo Quran seekhta aur sikhata hai.''
1453,"Hazrat Sehal bin Muaz Juhni apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney Quran padha aur jo us mein hai, usney us par amal kiya, to uskey maa baap ko qiyamat ke din eik taaj pehnaya jaeyga jiski roshni Suraj ki roshni se badh kar khoobsurat hogi , agar wo duniya mein tumharey gharon mein hota. (jab maa baap ka ye darja hai) to tumhara kya khayal hai khud us par amal kerney waley ka kya maqam hoga.''"
1454,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Quran padhta hai aur wo us mein mahir hai, wo aamaal nama likhney waley moazziz aur itaat guzar farishton ke sath hoga. aur jo shakhs Quran padhta hai, magar usey padhney mein mashaqqat hoti hai (atak atak kar padhta hai) to uskey liye do ajr hain.''"
1455,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''jo log Allah ke gharon mein se kisi ghar mein jama ho kar kitabullah ki tilawat kartey aur aapas mein uska dars aur muzaakra kartey hain to un par sakeenat nazil hoti hai, rehmat unhen dhanp leti hai, farishtey unhen apney gherey mein ley letey hain aur Shan Wala Allah unka zikr un mein karta hai jo uskey paas hotey hain.'' (malaaika muqarrebeen mein.)"
1456,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laye jabkey ham suffa mein they. aapney farmaya : ''tum mein se kaun pasand karta hai ke Bat'haan ya aqeeq wadi mein jaey aur wahan se moti tazi khoobsurat unchey kohan wali do oontniyaan ley aaye aur us mein kisi gunah ya qata' rahmi ka murtakib (gunahgaar) bhi na ho.'' kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham sab ye chahtey hain. aapney farmaya : ''tumhara har roz masjid ja kar kitabe Allah se do aayaten seekh lena, do oontniyon ke husool (hasil karne) se behtar hai, agar teen aayaten seekhey to teen oontniyon se behtar hai. isi tarah mazeed aayaton ki tadaad ke mutabiq oontniyon se behtar hai.'' Janab Abu-Ubaid ne ''Koma'' ka tarjama bayan kiya ke ''unchey kohan wali oontni.''"
1457,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(الحمد لله رب العالمين) Ummul-Quran hai, Ummul-Kitab aur Sabul-Masani hai.''"
1458,Hazrat Abu-Saeed bin Muallaa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unke paas se guzrey jabke wo Namaz padh rahey they. isliye aapney unko bulaya. wo kehtey hain ke maine apni Namaz mukammal ki phir aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua. aapney puchha : ''tum ko mujhey jawab deney se kya chiz maane (rukawat) hui'' (hazir kyon nahin huey?) unhoney kaha : main Namaz padh raha tha. aapney farmaya : ''kya Allah ne ye nahin farmaya : aey emaan walo ! Allah aur uskey Rasool ko jawab do jab wo tumhen bulaeyn aisi chiz ki taraf jo tumhen zindagi dey.'' (jo wo hukm den us par fauran amal paira (karne wale) ho jao.) ( phir farmaya : ( ''main tumhen masjid se janey se pehley Aazam (afzal) surat sikhaaun ga.'' Khalid ko shak hua hai ke hadees ke lafz ''من القرآن'' hain ya ''في القرآن'' (phir kuch der guzri to) maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney farmaya tha. . . . . . aapney farmaya. ... ''(wo surat) (الحمد لله رب العالمين) hai. ye (Sabul-Masani) hai jo mujhey di gaee hai aur Al-Quraane-Azeem (القرآن العظیم) hai.''
1459,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko saat aayaten di gaee hain jo baar baar dohrani jati hain aur badi lambi hain. aur Musa Alehissalam ko chhe di gaee thin. jab unhoney takhtiyon ko zameen par dal diya to un mein se do ko utha liya gaya aur chaar baqi rahin.
1460,Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se puchha : ''aey Abu Munzir ! tumhen Kitabe Allah main se sab se azeem aayat kaun si yaad hai? ''maine arz kiya : Allah aur uskey Rasool behtar jantey hain. aapney (phir) farmaya : ''aey Abu Munzir ! tumhen Kitabe Allah main se kaun si aayat yaad hai jo sab se azeem ho?'' maine arz kya : (اللہ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا هُوَ الْحَيُّ الْقَيُّومُ) is par aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne merey seeney mein maara aur farmaya : ''aey Abu Munzir ! tumhen ilm Mubarak ho.''
1461,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke eik shakhs ne doosrey ko suna ke wo (قل هو الله أحد) baar baar padh raha tha. subah hui to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur is baat ka aap se zikr kiya. ... . aur wo goya usko kam samajh raha tha. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''qasam hai us zaat ki jiskey haath mein meri jaan hai, be-shak ye tihai Quran ke barabar hai.''"
1462,Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki oontni ki nakel pakdey chal raha tha ke aapney mujh se farmaya : ''aey Aqba ! kya main tumhen do behtareen padhi gaee suraten na sikha dun.'' chunanche aapney mujhey ( قل أعوذ برب Falaq (aur ( قل أعوذ برب Naas ( sikhaeen. kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mehsoos kiya ke main un par koi bahut ziyada khush nahin hua hun. kaha : phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) namaze-Fajr ke liye utrey aur logon ko Namaz padhaai to Namaz mein yehi do suraten tilawat kin. jab aap Namaz se farigh huey to meri taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''aey Aqba ! kaisa paya.'' (in soorton ko?)
1463,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik baar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath chal raha tha, ham Jahfa aur Abwa ke darmiyan they ke aandhi aai aur sakht andhera chha gaya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (قل أعوذ برب الفلق) aur) قل أعوذ برب Naas ( padhney lagey aur farmaney lagey ''aey Aqba ! inki tilawat se tawwuz kiya karo. (Allah se panah manga karo.) kisi panah maangney waley ne in se badh kar afzal kalimaat se panah nahin maangi.'' Aqba kehtey hain : maine suna ke aap inhi soorton ke sath Namaz mein hamari imaamat farmatey they."
1464,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Sahibe Quran se kaha jaeyga ke padhta ja aur chadhta ja , aur usi tarah thehar thehar kar padh , jaisey ke duniya mein padha karta tha, jahan aakhiri aayat khatam kerega wahin tera maqam hoga.''"
1465,"Qatada kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat ke mutalliq sawal kiya to unhoney kaha : aap alfaz ko mud ke sath (khinch kar, lamba karkey) padha kartey they."
1466,"Ya'alaa bin Mamlak se riwayat hai ke unhoney Ummul-momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat aur aap ki Namaz ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney kaha : tumhara unki Namaz se kya muqabla? aap Namaz padhtey they phir usi qadr so jatey they jitna ke Namaz padhi hoti thi. phir uth kar Namaz padhtey they jis qadr ke soey hotey . phir so jatey jis qadr Namaz padhi hoti , yahan tak ke subah ho jati . unhoney aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat ka andaz bhi bataya ke eik eik harf alag alag hota tha."
1467,Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Fateh Makka ke din dekha ke aap apni oontni par Sawar Sura Fateh padh rahey they aur tarjeea' se (bar bar) padh rahey they.
1468,Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apni aawaazon se Quran ko zeenat do.''
1469,"Abul-Waleed Tiyalisi ki sanad se Hazrat Saad bin Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, . . . . aur Yazid (raawi) ki sanad mein Hazrat Saeed bin Abi Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai aur Quteba ne bhi yehi kaha ke meri kitab mein Saeed bin Abi Saeed hai. ... unhoney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Quran ko achchhi aawaz se na padhey wo ham mein se nahin.''"
1470,Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya. ... aur mazkura baala hadees ke misl (jaisi) bayan kiya.
1471,"Ubaidullah bin Abi Yazid ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat Abu-Lubaba (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey paas se guzrey , ham unke peechhey ho liye , yahan tak ke wo apney ghar mein dakhil ho gaey to ham bhi andar gaey . ham ne dekha ke bada hi puraanaa ghar aur unki apni haalat bhi had se zyada saada si thi. maine un se suna, kehtey they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna aap farmatey they : ''jo shakhs Quran karim ko achchhi awaaz se na padhey wo ham mein se nahin .'' (raawi hadees Abdul-jabbaar ne) kaha : maine ibne-abi Mulaika se kaha : agar wo khush aawaz na ho to? unhoney kaha : jahan tak mumkin ho aawaz ko umda banaey."
1472,Muhammad bin Sulaiman Anbari bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Wakee aur ibne-Uena (Reh.) mazkura hadees ke maani ye letey they ke us se murad ''istighnaa'' (beniyazi) hai.
1473,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Shan Wala Allah kisi chiz ko is qadr kaan laga kar nahin sunta , jitna ke kisi khush-alhan (achchhi aawaz) ke sath Nabi ke buland aawaz se Quran padhney par kaan lagata hai.''"
1474,"Hazrat Saad bin Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Quran padh kar bhula dey , wo qiyamat ke roz Allah se is haalat mein milega ke wo juzaam zada hoga.''"
1475,"Abdur-Rehman bin Abdul-Qaari kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko suna, wo bayan kartey they ke maine Hisham bin Hakeem bin Hizam ko Sura Furqaan padhtey suna, magar uski qirat iskey khilaf thi jo main padhta tha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hi ne mujhey ye surat padhaai thi. qarib tha ke main us par jaldi karta (aur jhapat padta) magar maine usko mohlat di yahan tak ke wo farigh hua , phir maine uski gardan apni chadar se pakad li aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley aaya . maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine isko Sura Furqaan padhtey suna hai aur ye uskey khilaf padhta hai jo aapney mujhey padhaai hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : ''padho.'' chunanche usney usi qirat mein padhi jo maine us se suni thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''isi tarah utaari gaee hai.'' phir mujhey farmaya : ''padho'' chunanche maine bhi padhi, to aapney farmaya : ''aisey hi utaari gaee hai.'' phir farmaya : ''bila-shuba ye Quran saat huroof par nazil kiya gaya hai, to is se jo aasan lagey padho.''"
1476,Zohri (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke ye (saat mukhtalif) huroof eik hi maani aur mafhoom ke hamil hotey hain. in se halal aur haram mein koi ikhtilaf nahin hota.
1477,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey Ubai ! mujhey Quran padhaya gaya to kaha gaya : eik harf par) padhna pasand kartey ho) ya do harfon par? to wo farishta jo merey sath tha, usney kaha ke kaho : do harfon par. to maine kaha : do harfon par. phir mujhey kaha gaya : do harfon par ya teen harfon par ? wo farishta jo merey sath tha, usney kaha ke kaho , teen par . maine kaha : teen harfon par , yahan tak ke baat saat harfon tak pahunchi . phir kaha : un mein se her eik harf shafi kafi hai. agar aap (سميعا عليما) ki bajaey (عزيزا حكيما) keh den to sahih hai, magar kisi aayat azab ko rehmat ke sath ya kisi aayat rehmat ko azab ke sath na badlen.''"
1478,"Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qabeela bani ghifaar ke taalaab ke paas they ke aap par Jibrael Alehissalam nazil huey aur farmaya : be-shak Allah taala aap ko ye hukm deta hai ke apni ummat ko eik harf par Quran padhaen. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kaha : ''main Shan Wale Allah se mafi aur maghfirat ka saail hun, kyonkey meri ummat uski taqat nahin rakhti . ''phir Jibrael Alehissalam dusri baar aaye aur pehley ki manind zikr kiya, yahan tak ke saat harfon tak pahunchey . farmaya : Allah tumhen hukm deta hai ke apni ummat ko) kalame Allah ( saat harfon par padhaen , jis harf par bhi wo padhengey , sahi hoga."
1479,"Hazrat Nauman bin Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dua ibadat hi hai. tumharey Rab ne farmaya hai : mujhey pukaro , main qubul karunga.''"
1480,"Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ke eik sahibzadey kehtey hain, merey walid ne mujhey suna ke main is tarah se dua kar raha tha : aey Allah ! main tujh se jannat ka sawal karta hun aur uski nematon ka aur raunqon ka aur ye aur ye . aur jahannam se panah maangta hun aur uski zanjeeron aur tauqon se aur uski aisi aisi balaaun se. to unhoney kaha : bete ! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : ''an-qareeb kuchh log hongey jo dua mein mubaalgha karengey.'' to khayal rakho kahin un mein se na bin jana . agar tujhey jannat mil gaee to uski tamam khairaat tumhen mil jaeyngi . aur agar jahannam se bach gaey to uski tamam aafaton se bhi bach jao gey."
1481,"Sahibe Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Fazaala bin Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik shakhs ko Namaz mein dua kartey huey suna ke usney Allah ki hamd aur sanaa na ki thi aur na Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye durood padha tha, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usney jaldi ki.'' phir usko bulaya aur usey ya kisi doosrey se farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Namaz padhey to pehley apney Rab ki hamd aur sanaa bayan karey, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye durood padhey , uskey baad jo chahey dua karey.''"
1482,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Jaame duaen pasand farmaya kartey they aur uskey alawa ko chhod detey they.
1483,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se koi aisey dua mat karey ke ya Allah ! mujhey bakhsh dey agar chahey to . ya Allah ! mujh par rehem farma agar chahey to . jo maangna hai azeemat aur pukhtagi se maango . Allah ko koi majboor nahin kar sakta.''
1484,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul (naqal hui) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum mein se eik ki dua qubul hoti rehti hai jab tak ke wo jaldi na karey. yani yun kahey ke maine dua ki magar qubul nahin hui .''
1485,"Muhammad bin Kab Qurzi Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''deewaron ko (kapdon waghaira sey) mat dhaanpo. jis shakhs ne apney bhai ki kitab (ya tehreer) mein uski ijazat ke baghair dekha wo aag mein dekhta hai. Allah se maango to hatheliyan phela kar maango , haathon ki pusht se mat maango aur jab tum dua se farigh ho to unhen apney chehron par pher liya karo . Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke ye hadees Muhammad bin Kab se kaee sanadon se marwi (bayan) hai aur sabhi zaeef hain. aur ye (mazkura) sanad un sab mein se achhi hai, magar ye bhi zaeef hai."
1486,"Abu-Bahriya Sakuni Malik bin Yasar Sakuni Aufee se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum Allah se sawal karo (dua karo) to apney haathon ki hatheliyon se manga karo, haathon ki pusht se na manga karo . Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Sulaiman bin Abdul-Hameed ne kaha ke hamarey ilm ke mutabiq Malik bin Yasar ko sharf sahabiyat hasil hai."
1487,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha aap apney haathon ki hatheliyon ki janib se aur pusht ki janib se bhi dua kartey they.
1488,"Hazrat Salman Farsi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba tumhara Rab bahut haya wala aur sakhi hai. banda jab uski taraf apney haath uthata hai to usey haya aati hai ke unhen khaali lauta dey.''"
1489,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai kaha ke sawal (yani dua ka adab ( ye hai ke tum apney haath apney kandhon ke barabar ya uskey qarib buland karo . aur istighfar ye hai ke apni eik ungli se ishara karo aur ibtihal (ijz w inkisaar) yun hai ke apney dono haathon ko lamba karo.
1490,Abbas bin Abdullah bin Maabad bin Abbas ne usi mazkura hadees ko bayan kiya to us mein kaha ke ibtihaal (ijz w inkisaar aur dua mein mubaalgha) aisey hai aur (amalan) apney dono haath uthaey aur unki pusht ko apney chehrey ki taraf kiya.
1491,"Abbas bin Abdullah bin Maabad bin Abbas apney bhai Ibrahim bin Abdullah sey, wo Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya. . . . aur usi ki manind zikr kiya."
1492,Saaib bin Yazid apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab dua kartey aur apney haath uthatey to apney chehrey par pher liya kartey they.
1493,"Abdullah bin Barida se riwayat hai ke unke walid ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik shakhs ko dua kartey suna wo keh raha tha : (اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَسْأَلُكَ أَنِّي أَشْهَدُ أَنَّكَ أَنْتَ اللَّهُ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا أَنْتَ الْأَحَدُ الصَّمَدُ الَّذِي لَمْ يَلِدْ وَلَمْ يُولَدْ وَلَمْ يَكُنْ لَهُ كُفُوًا أَحَدٌ ) ''aey Allah ! main tujh se sawal karta hun is bina par ke main gawahi deta hun ke to hi Allah hai. terey siwa aur koi mabud nahin. to akela hai, be-niyaz hai jisney na janaa aur na janaa hi gaya aur koi bhi uski barabari kerney wala nahin.''  to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tu ne Allah se uskey us naam se sawal kiya hai ke jab us se is naam se manga jaey to inayat farmata hai, dua ki jaey to qubul karta hai.''"
1494,"Malik bin Mighwal ne yehi hadees bayan ki, is mein kaha : ''be-shak usney Shan Wale Allah se uskey badey naam ke ba-wastey se sawal kiya hai.''"
1495,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas baithey huey they aur eik aadmi Namaz padh raha tha. usney dua ki : ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَسْأَلُكَ بِأَنَّ لَكَ الْحَمْدُ , لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا أَنْتَ الْمَنَّانُ بَدِيعُ السَّمَوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضِ , يَا ذَالْجَلَالِ وَالْإِكْرَامِ يَا حَيُّ يَا قَيُّومُ ) ''aey Allah ! main tujh se sawal karta hun is liye ke teri hi tareef hai, terey siwa koi mabud nahin, to be-inteha ehsan kerney wala hai, aasman aur zameen ko be-mada aur be-namoona paida kerney wala hai. aey jalal aur ikram waley ! aey zinda ! aey nigrani kerney waley !''  to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tehqiq usney Allah se uskey us azeem naam ke wastey se dua ki hai jis se dua ki jaey to wo qubul karta hai, manga jaey to deta hai.''"
1496,"Shehar bin Hoshab, Hazrat Asma binte Yazeed (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah ka Ism A'zm (bada naam) in do aayaton mein hai : ( وَإِلَهُكُمْ إِلَهٌ وَاحِدٌ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا هُوَ الرَّحْمَنُ الرَّحِيمُ ) aur sura Aale-Imran ki ibtidaai (shuruati) aayat mein (الم اللَّهُ لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا هُوَ الْحَيُّ الْقَيُّومُ)"
1497,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke unka eik lihaaf chori ho gaya to wo chor par bad-dua kerney lagin. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaney lagey : ''uskey gunah ko halka mat kar. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : (لا تسبخي) ke maani (لا تخففي) hain, yani ''halka na kar, kam na kar.''"
1498,Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Umra kerney ki rukhsat chahi . aapney mujhey ijazat de-di aur farmaya : ''merey piyaarey bhai ! hamein apni dua mein mat bhoolna.'' aapney aisey lafz farmaai ke mujhey unke badley duniya bhi miley to pasand nahin. Shoba kehtey hain ke main baad mein Janab Aasim se Madina mein mila to unhoney mujhey ye hadees bayan ki. unke lafz they : ''merey azeez bhai ! hamein apni dua mein shareek rakhna.''
1499,"Hazrat Saad ibne-Abi Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey paas se guzrey aur main apni do ungliyan uthaey dua kar raha tha to aapney farmaya : ''eik se, eik se.'' aur angusht shahadat se ishara farmaya."
1500,"Aaisha binte Saad bin Abi Waqas apney walid ( Hazrat Saad (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat karti hain ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath eik aurat ke paas aaye jabke us aurat ke samney guthliyaan thin ya kankariyaan , wo unke sath tasbih padh rahi thi. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen wo chiz na bataun jo tumharey liye is se aasan tar ya afzal ho? ''to aapney farmaya : (سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ عَدَدَ مَا خَلَقَ فِي السَّمَاءِ . .  الخ) ''Allah ki tasbih hai us makhluq ki tadaad mein jo usney aasman mein paida ki . Allah ki tasbih hai us makhluq ki tadaad mein jo usney zameen mein paida ki . Allah ki tasbih hai us makhluq ki tadaad mein jo usney un dono ke beech paida ki, Allah ki tasbih hai us makhluq ki tadaad mein jo wo paida kerega. aur (الله أكبر) usi ke jaisi aur (الحمد الله) usi ke jiasi aur (لا إله إلا الله) usi ke jaisi aur) َلَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّةَ إِلَّا بِاللَّهِ) usi ke jaisi."
1501,Hazrat Yaseera (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen (sahaabiyaat ko) hukm diya tha ke wo Allah ki takbir ( الله أكبر ( taqdees ( سبحان الملك القدوس) aur tahleel (لا إله إلا الله) ki pabandi ikhtiyar keren aur ye ke apni ungliyon par shumar kiya keren kyonkey un se sawal hoga aur ye bulwaai jaeyngi .
1502,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu anha) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha ke aap apney haath (ki ungliyon) par tasbih shumar kartey they. (ustad) ibne Qudama ne wazahat ki ke apney daain haath se.
1503,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) , Hazrat Juweriya (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan se nikley . ... . is se pehley unka naam ''barra'' ( nek aur saalah) tha. aur aapney unka naam tabdeel kar diya tha. ... . aap unke yahan se nikley aur wo apney musalley par thin , phir wapis tashrif laye to ( dekha ke) wo apney musalley hi par hain. aapney puchha : ''kya tum us waqt se apney musalley hi par ho? ''wo kehney lagin : haan ! aapney farmaya : ''maine tumharey ( yahaan se janey ke) baad chaar kalimaat teen baar kahey hain, agar unko tumhari tasbeehaat aur zikr se wazan kya jaey to ye ( merey kalmaat ( bhari ho jaeyngey. yani ( سُبْحَانَ اللَّهِ وَبِحَمْدِهِ عَدَدَ خَلْقِهِ وَرِضَا نَفْسِهِ وَزِنَةَ عَرْشِهِ وَمِدَادَ كَلِمَاتِهِ ) ''pakizgi hai Allah ki uski taareefon ke sath , is qadr jitni ke uski makhluq hai aur itni ke us se wo razi ho jaey aur uskey arsh ke wazan ke barabar aur is qadr jitni ke uskey kalimaat ki roshnai hai.''"
1504,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye maal aur daulat waley to ajr aur sawab ley gaey (aur ham khaali reh gaey !) wo namaazen padhtey hain jaisey ke ham padhtey hain, wo rozey rakhtey hain jaisey ke ham rakhtey hain aur unke paas zayed amwaal hain jo wo sadqa kartey hain lekin hamarey paas nahin hain ke sadqa karen. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''abu-Zar ! kya main tumhen aisey kalimaat na sikha dun jin sey tum apney se aagey badhney walon ko pa lo aur peechhey rehney waley tumhen na pa saken siwaey iske ke koi tumhari tarah ka amal karey? ''kaha : haan aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney farmaya : ''har Namaz ke baad tentis ( 33 ( baar ( الله اكبر ( tentis ( 33 ( baar ( الحمد الله (aur tentis (33) baar (سبحان الله) kaha karo aur unka ikhtitaam ( لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لَا شَرِيكَ لَهُ لَهُ الْمُلْكُ وَلَهُ الْحَمْدُ وَهُوَ عَلَى كُلِّ شَيْءٍ قَدِيرٌ ( par ho, is se uskey gunah bakhsh diye jaeyngey agar-che samandar ki jhaag ke barabar hon.''"
1505,"Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Mughira ko khat likha aur puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaz se salam ke baad kya padha kartey they? to Hazrat Mughira ne Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf likhwa bheja ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) padha kartey they : (لا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَحْدَهُ لا شَرِيكَ لَهُ لَهُ الْمُلْكُ وَلَهُ الْحَمْدُ وَهُوَ عَلَى كُلِّ شَيْءٍ قَدِيرٌ - اللهم لا مَانِعَ لِمَا أَعْطَيْتَ وَلَا مُعْطِيَ لِمَا مَنَعْتَ وَلَا يَنْفَعُ ذَاالْجَدِّ مِنْكَ الْجَدُّ) ''Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud nahin, wo akela hai, uska koi sajhi nahin. mulk usi ka hai. tareef usi ki hai aur wo her chiz par qudrat rakhta hai. aey Allah ! jo to inayat farma dey usey koi nahin rok sakta aur jo to rok ley wo koi dey nahin sakta aur kisi bhi maaldaar ko terey muqabley mein uska maal fayda nahin dey sakta.''"
1506,"Abu-Zubair kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko member par ye kehtey huey suna ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Namaz se phirtey (yani salam ke baad) to ye padha kartey they : (لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله الحمد وهو على كل شيء قدير ، لا إله إلا الله مخلصين له الدين ولو كره الكافرون ، أهل النعمة والفضل والثناء الحسن ، لا إله إلا الله مخلصين له الدين ولو كره الكافرون) ''eik Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud nahin. wo akela hai. uska koi shareek nahin. mulk usi ka hai, tareef usi ki hai aur wo her cheez par qadir hai. Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud nahin. ham khalis usi ki itaat kartey hain, chahey (chaahe) kafiron ko ye napasand ho. (aey Allah ! ( to hi nemat aur fazal wala aur behtareen tareef ka mustahiq hai. Allah ke siwa aur koi mabud nahin ! ham khalis usi ki itaat kartey hain chahey kafiron ko ye napasand hi ho.''"
1507,Abu-Zubair kehtey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) har Namaz ke baad (لا إله إلا الله وحده . .  الخ) padha kartey they aur mazkura baala hadees ki manind dua zikr ki aur ye izafa kya : (ولا حول wla قوة إلا بالله ، لا إله إلا الله ، لا نعبد إلا إياه له النعمة . . ۔ ) aur baqiiya hadees bayan ki .
1508,"Hazrat Zaid bin Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna ke aap Namaz ke baad ye padha kartey they : (اللَّهُمَّ ! رَبَّنَا وَ رَبَّ كُلِّ شَيْءٍ أَنَا شَهِيدٌ أَنَّكَ أَنْتَ الرَّبُّ وَحْدَكَ لَا شَرِيكَ لَكَ ، اللَّهُمَّ ! رَبَّنَا وَ رَبَّ كُلِّ شَيْءٍ أَنَا شَهِيدٌ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُكَ وَرَسُولُكَ ، اللَّهُمَّ رَبَّنَا و َرَبَّ كُلِّ شَيْءٍ ، أَنَا شَهِيدٌ أَنَّ الْعِبَادَ كُلَّهُمْ إِخْوَةٌ ، اللَّهُمَّ رَبَّنَا وَ رَبَّ كُلِّ شَيْءٍ اجْعَلْنِي مُخْلِصًا لَكَ وَأَهْلِي فِي كُلِّ سَاعَةٍ فِي الدُّنْيَا وَالْآخِرَةِ يَا ذَا الْجَلَالِ وَالْإِكْرَامِ اسْمَعْ وَاسْتَجِبْ . اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ الْأَكْبَرُ ، اللَّهُمَّ ! نُورَ السَّمَوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضِ ، اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ الْأَكْبَرُ ، حَسْبِيَ اللَّهُ وَنِعْمَ الْوَكِيلُ ، اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ الْأَكْبَرُ ) ''aey Allah ! hamarey rab aur har har cheez ke Rab ! main gawah hun ke to akela hi Rab hai. tera koi saajhi nahin. aey Allah ! hamarey Rab aur har har cheez ke Rab ! main gawah hun ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) terey bandey aur Rasool hain. aey Allah ! hamarey Rab aur har har cheez ke Rab ! main gawah hun ke sarey bandey ( eik doosrey ke) bhai hain. aey Allah ! hamarey Rab aur har har cheez ke Rab ! mujhey aur merey ehle ko duniya aur aakhirat ke andar her ghadi mein apna mukhlis banaey rakh . aey jalal aur ikram waley ! meri dua sun aur qubul farma . Allah sab se bada hai, bahut hi bada . aey Allah ! aasmano aur zameen ka Noor hai.'' ... Sulaiman bin Dawud ne '' Noor '' ke bajaey ''Rab'' ka lafz kaha hai. (yani (aey aasmano aur zameen ke Rab . ... Allah sab se bada hai, bahut hi bada . mujhey Allah kafi hai aur wo behtareen karsaz hai. Allah sab se bada hai, bahut hi bada.''"
1509,"Hazrat Ali bin Abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai wo kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Namaz se salam phertey , to ye padha kartey they : (اللهم اغْفِرْلِي ما قَدَّمْتُ وَمَا أَخَّرْتُ وَمَا أَسْرَرْتُ وَمَا أَعْلَنْتُ وَمَا أَسْرَفْتُ وَمَا أَنْتَ أَعْلَمُ بِهِ مِنِّي أَنْتَ الْمُقَدِّمُ وَأَنْتَ الْمُؤَخِّرُ لا إِلَهَ إِلَّا أَنْتَ) ''aey Allah ! mujhey bakhsh dey wo taqseeraat (gunah) jo maine pehley kiye , jo baad mein kiye , jo poshida kiye aur jinhen zaahiran kiya aur jo main had se guzarta raha , aur wo jinkey mutalliq to mujh se ziyada ba-khabar hai, to hi (jisey chahey) aagey kerney wala aur (jisey chahey) peechhey rakhney wala hai. (neki ki taufiq deta hai ya mehroom kar deta hai.) terey alawa aur koi mabud nahin.''"
1510,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai wo kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye dua kya kartey they : (رَبِّ أَعِنِّي وَلَا تُعِنْ عَلَيَّ وَانْصُرْنِي وَلَا تَنْصُرْ عَلَيَّ وَامْكُرْلِي وَلَا تَمْكُرْ عَلَيَّ وَاهْدِنِي وَيَسِّرْ هُدَايَ إِلَيَّ وَانْصُرْنِي عَلَى من بَغَى عَلَيَّ اللهم ! اجْعَلْنِي لَكَ شَاكِرًا لَكَ ذَاكِرًا لَكَ رَاهِبًا لَكَ مِطْوَاعًا إِلَيْكَ مُخْبِتًا أَوْ مُنِيبًا رَبِّ ! تَقَبَّلْ تَوْبَتِي وَاغْسِلْ حَوْبَتِي وَأَجِبْ دَعْوَتِي وَثَبِّتْ حُجَّتِي وَاهْدِ قَلْبِي وَسَدِّدْ لِسَانِي وَاسْلُلْ سَخِيمَةَ قَلْبِي) ''aey merey Rab ! meri madad farma , merey khilaf kisi ki madad na kar) jo mujhey teri itaat se rok dey .) meri nusrat farma , merey khilaf kisi ki nusrat na kar. merey haq mein tadbeer farma, merey khilaf tadbeer na kar. meri rehnumai farma aur hidayat ko merey liye aasan farma dey . aur jo merey khilaf baghawat karey uskey muqabley mein meri madad farma , ya Allah ! mujhey bana dey apna shukr guzar , apna zikr kerney wala, tujhi se darney wala, had se zyada itaat guzar aur bahut hi tawaazeh kerney wala . aey merey Rab ! meri tauba qubul kar ley . meri khataeyn dho dal . meri dua qubul farma . meri hujjat qaaim farma dey . merey dil ko hidayat dey (aur hidayat par Sabit qadam rakh ( meri zaban ko haq par seedhey rakh aur merey dil se mail kuchail (bughz , hasad aur keena waghera) nikal dey.''"
1511,Amr bin Murra ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya aur : ( ويسِّرِ الهُدى إلي ( kaha ( هداي ( nahin kaha.
1512,Ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab salam phertey to padhtey : (اللَّهُمَّ أَنْتَ السَّلَامُ و َمِنْكَ السَّلَامُ تَبَارَكْتَ يَا ذَاالْجَلَالِ وَالْإِكْرَامِ) ''aey Allah to ( sarapa ( salamti hai aur tujhi se salamti ( hasil hoti ( hai. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Sufiyan ne Amr bin Murra se suna hai. aur muhaddeseen ka kehna hai ke unhoney un se atthaara ahadis suni hain.
1513,Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu)) maula Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Namaz se uth kar jana chahtey to teen baar istighfar ( أستغفر الله ( kehtey they. phir uskey baad padhtey ( اللهم أنت السلام . . . . . الخ (aur hadees Hazrat Aaysha ki hadees ke ham-maani bayan ki .
1514,"Saiyedna Abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo istighfar ko ikhtiyar kar ley wo '' Misr '' ( israr kerney waley ( logon mein nahin, chahey (chaahe) eik din mein sattar baar gunah ko dohraae.''"
1515,Hazrat Agrar Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai. ... . Musaddad ki riwayat mein hai ke unko sharfe sohbat hasil tha. ... . ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''merey dil par bhi parda sa aa jata hai aur main Allah se eik eik din mein sau-sau baar istighfar karta hun.''
1516,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke bila-shuba ham shumar kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik eik majlis mein so so baar ye kalma dohraatey they : ( رَبِّ اغْفِرْلِي وَتُبْ عَلَيَّ إِنَّكَ أَنْتَ التَّوَّابُ الرَّحِيمُ ) ''aey merey Rab ! mujhey bakhsh dey aur) rehmat ke sath ( meri taraf ruju farma . bila-shuba to bahut ziyada ruju farmaney wala aur rehem kerney wala hai.''
1517,"Hazrat Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) (maula Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''jo shakhs yun kehta hai : ( أَسْتَغْفِرُ اللَّهَ الَّذِي لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا هُوَ الْحَيَّ الْقَيُّومَ وَأَتُوبُ إِلَيْهِ )''main maafi maangta hun Allah sey, wo zaat ke uskey alawa aur koi mabud nahin, wo zinda hai aur nigrani kerney wala hai. aur main usi ki taraf tauba aur ruju karta hun.'' to usko bakhsh diya jata hai agar-che wo jihad se bhi bhaagaa ho.''"
1518,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jisney istighfar ka iltizaam wajib kiya, Allah taala uskey liye her tangi se nikalney ki raah aur her gham se rahat ka saman paida farma dega . aur aisey aisey maqamat se rizq mohaiyya farmaeyga jis ka usey weham aur guman bhi na hoga.''"
1519,Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb bayan kartey hain ke Janab Qatada ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kaun si dua ziyada kiya kartey they? unhoney kaha : aap ki aksar dua ye hua karti thi : (اللَّهُمَّ رَبَّنَا آتِنَا فِي الدُّنْيَا حَسَنَةً وَفِي الْآخِرَةِ حَسَنَةً وَقِنَا عَذَابَ النَّار ) ''aey Allah ! aey hamarey Rab ! hamein duniya mein her tarah ki bhalaiyan inayat farma aur aakhirat mein bhi tamam nekiyan aur khairaat se sarfaraaz farma aur aag ke azab se mehfooz rakh.'' Ziyad ne mazeed kaha ke Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) jab koi dua karna chahtey to inhi alfaz se dua kartey aur jab koi ( khas ( dua karna chahtey to is mein usey bhi shamil kar letey they.
1520,Abu-Umama bin Sehal bin Haneef apney walid se riwayat kartey hain wo kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis shakhs ne sachchey dil se shahadat ka sawal kiya Allah taala usko shuhda ki manaazil tak pahuncha dega chahey (chaahe) apney bistar hi par usey maut aaye .''
1521,"Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) farmatey they ke main aisa shakhs tha ke jab main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se koi hadees sunta tu Allah taala mujhey us se jo chahta faayda inayat farmata . aur jab koi aur sahabi hadees bayan karta , to main us se qasam leta tha aur jab wo qasam uthata to main uski tasdeeq karta tha. kaha : mujh se Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadees bayan ki aur unhoney sach kaha, unhoney bayan kiya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna aap farma rahey they : '' koi banda aisa nahin jo koi gunah kar baithey phir wuzu karey achhi tarah , phir khada ho aur do rakatein padhey aur Allah se istighfar karey, magar Allah usey maaf kar deta hai. phir aapney ye aayat padhi : (وَالَّذِينَ إِذَا فَعَلُوا فَاحِشَةً أَوْ ظَلَمُوا أَنْفُسَهُمْ ذَكَرُوا اللَّهَ فَاسْتَغْفَرُوا لِذُنُوبِهِمْ وَمَنْ يَغْفِرُ الذُّنُوبَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ وَلَمْ يُصِرُّوا عَلَى ما فَعَلُوا وَهُمْ يَعْلَمُونَ) ''muttaqi wo log hain jo agar kabhi koi be-hayai ka kaam keren ya apni jaanon par koi zulm kar baithein , tu Allah ko yaad kartey aur apney gunahon ki maafi maangtey hain. aur Allah ke siwa aur kaun hai jo gunah bakhsh dey . aur ye log jantey boojhtey apney kiye par nahin udtey aur na israr kartey hain.''"
1522,"Hazrat Muaz bin Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unka haath pakda aur farmaya : ''aey Muaz ! qasam Allah ki ! mujhey tum se mohabbat hai.'' phir farmaya : ''aey Muaz ! main tumhen wasiyat karta hun ke kisi Namaz ke baad ye dua hergiz tarak na karna : (اللَّهُمَّ أَعِنِّي عَلَى ذِكْرِكَ وَشُكْرِكَ وَحُسْنِ عِبَادَتِكَ) ''aey Allah ! apna zikr karney , shukr karney aur behtareen andaz main apni ibadat karney mein meri madad farma.'' chunanche Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye wasiyat (apney shagrid) Sunabihi ko ki aur phir Sunabihi ne ye wasiyat (apney shagrid) Abu-Abdur-Rehman ko ki."
1523,Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya tha ke her Namaz ke baad muawwizaat padha karun.
1524,Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko ye baat pasand thi ke dua ke kalimaat teen teen baar dohraaen aur teen baar istighfar karen.
1525,"Hazrat Asma binte-Umais (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : ''kya main tumhen aisey kalimaat na sikha dun jo tum pareshani ki soorat mein padha karo . ... yani ( أَللَّهُ أَللَّهُ رَبِّي لَا أُشْرِكُ بِهِ شَيْئًا ) ''Allah , Allah hi mera Rab hai main uskey sath kisi chiz ko shareek nahin banati (banata).'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke raawi hadees Hilal, ye umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) ka maula hai. aur ibne Jaafar se murad Abdullah bin Jaafar hai."
1526,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke main eik safar mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha. jab ham Madina ke qarib pahunchey to logon ne ( الله أكبر ( ) الله أكبر ( . kehna shuru kar diya aur apni aawazen oonchi kin , to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''logo ! tum kisi behrey ya ghayeb ko nahin pukar rahey ho, be-shak jisey tum pukartey ho wo tumharey aur tumhari sawaariyon ki gardanon ke darmiyan ( nihayat qarib hai, lihaza cheekhney chillaney ki zarurat nahin.) hai.'' phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Musa ! kya main tumhen jannat ka eik khazana na bataun ?'' maine arz kiya : wo kya hai? farmaya : (لَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّةَ إِلَّا بِاللَّهِ ) ''kisi burai se bachna aur door rehna aur kisi neki aur khair ki himmat paanaa Allah ke baghair mumkin nahin.''"
1527,"Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke wo log Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath they aur eik ghaati par chadh rahey they eik aadmi jab bhi kisi ghaati par chadhta to khoob oonchi aawaz se kehta : (لا إله إلا الله والله أكبر) to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum kisi behrey ya ghayeb ko nahin pukartey ho.'' ( wo sunney wala aur qarib hai, chillatey kyon ho?) phir farmaya : ''aey Abdullah bin Qais ! '' (Abu-Musa Ash'ari (aur mazkura hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya."
1528,"Abu-Usman ne , Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) se yehi hadees riwayat ki hai aur us mein kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' logo ! apney aap par rehem karo) chillaao nahin).''"
1529,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs : ( رَضِيتُ بِاللَّهِ رَبًّا وَبِالْإِسْلَامِ دِينًا , وَ بِمُحَمَّدٍ رَسُولًا ) ''main Allah ke Rab honey par , Islam ke deen honey par aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Rasool honey par razi hun.'' kahe uskey liye jannat wajib ho gaee.''"
1530,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs eik baar mujh par durood padhta hai, Allah taala us par das rahmaten nazil karta hai.''"
1531,"Hazrat Aus bin Aus (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumharey afzal dino mein se Jumey ka din fazilat wala hai, so us din mujh par kasrat se durood padha karo . bila-shuba tumhara durood mujh par pesh kiya jata hai.'' Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamara durood aap par kaisey pesh kiya jaeyga halanke aap ka jism ( qabr mein) boseedah ho chuka hoga ? farmaya : '' be-shak Allah taala ne anbiya (Alaihimussalam) ke jism zameen par haram kar diye hain.''"
1532,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''apney aap ko bad-dua na do , apni aulad ko bad-dua na do , apney khaadimon ko bad-dua na do aur apney maalon ko bad-dua na do , aisa na ho ke wo Allah ki taraf se ata aur qubuliyat ki ghadi ho ( udhar tum koi bad-dua karo ke Allah taala usey ( tumharey liye qubul kar ley . Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke ye hadees muttasil hai, Ubaada bin Waleed bin Ubada ne Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat ki hai."
1533,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik aurat ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha : merey aur merey shohar ke liye duaaey rehmat farma dijiye , to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah tujh par aur terey shohar par apni rahmatein (aur barkaten ( nazil farmaai .''"
1534,"Umme-Dardaa (Reh.) bayan karti hain ke merey aaqa Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna tha, aap farmatey they : ''jab koi shakhs apney bhai ke liye ghaaibaana dua karta hai to farishtey kehtey hain, aameen (aey Allah ! qubul farma) aur tujhey bhi yehi kuch hasil ho.''"
1535,Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bahut jald qubul honey wali dua ye hai ke insan kisi ghair maujood ke liye ghaaibaana dua karey.''
1536,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''teen duaon ke qubul honey mein shak nahin. baap ki dua , musafir ki dua aur mazloom ki dua.''"
1537,Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash'ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab kisi qaum se koi andesha hota to is tarah dua kartey : ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنَّا نَجْعَلُكَ فِي نُحُورِهِمْ وَنَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ شُرُورِهِمْ ) ''aey Allah ham tujhey unke muqabley mein pesh kartey hain aur unki shararaton se teri panah mein aatey hain.''
1538,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anha) bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamein istikhaare ki (is ehtimam sey) taaleem farmatey they jaisey ke Quran ki koi surat . aap hamein farmatey ke jab tum mein se koi kisi kaam ka irada karey to usey chahiye ke farzon ke alawa do rakaten padhey aur yun dua karey : ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَسْتَخِيرُكَ بِعِلْمِكَ وَأَسْتَقْدِرُكَ بِقُدْرَتِكَ . ... الخ ) ''aey Allah ! main terey ilm ke wastey se khair aur bhalai chahta hun. aur teri qudrat ke wastey se qudrat talab karta hun. aur terey fazale-azeem ka sawal karta hun. be-shak to qudrat rakhta hai aur main qudrat nahin rakhta. to janta hai aur main nahin janta . aur to tamam ghaibon aur poshida umur (baton) se puri tarah ba-khabar hai. aey Allah ! agar terey ilm mein ye maamla ( yahan apney kaam ka naam ley ( merey deen , duniya , aakhirat aur anjam ke lihaz se behtar hai to usey merey haq mein muqaddar farma dey , usey merey liye aasan kar dey aur mujhey us mein barkat dey . aur agar ye maamla ( yahan apney kaam ka naam ley ( terey ilm ke mutabiq merey liye bura hai, deen , duniya , aakhirat ya anjam ke lihaz sey, to mujhey us se pher dey aur usko mujh se pher dey aur merey liye khair muqaddar farma dey jahan bhi ho, phir mujhey us par razi kar dey.''  raawi ne kaha ya shayad ( خَيْرٌ ا لِي فِي دِينِي وَمَعَاشِي وَ مَعَادِي وَعَاقِبَةِ أَمْرِي ( ki bajaey ( فِي عَاجِلِ أَمْرِي وَآجِلِهِ (ke lafz farmaai ''yani merey maamley mein ye jald ya der se . ... behtar ho.'' ibne Muslima aur ibne Esa is sanad ko lafz ''عن (an)'' se bayan kartey hain. ''عن (an) Muhammad bin المنكدر an (an) Jabir''."
1539,"Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) paanch baaton se Allah ki panah manga kartey they buzdili , bakheeli , intehai budhapey aur laachaari ki umr sey, seeney ke fitney se ( hasad , keena aur burey akhlaq aur aqaaid sey) aur azabe-qabr se."
1540,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye dua kiya kartey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنَ الْعَجْزِ وَالْكَسَلِ وَالْجُبْنِ وَالْبُخْلِ وَالْهَرَمِ وَأَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ عَذَابِ الْقَبْرِ , وَأَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ فِتْنَةِ الْمَحْيَا وَالْمَمَاتِ ) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun aajiz aa janey sey, kasl-mandi aur susti sey, buzdili, bakheeli aur intehai budhapey se. aur teri panah chahta hun qabr ke azab se aur zindagi aur maut ke fitney se.''"
1541,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat kiya karta tha aur main aap ko b-kasrat sunta tha ke aap ye dua kartey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ انی أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنَ الْهَمِّ وَالْحَزَنِ وَضَلْعِ الدَّيْنِ وَغَلَبَةِ الرِّجَالِ ) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun pareshani aur gham sey, qarzey ke bojh se aur logon ( zalimon (ke ghalbey aur zor aawri se.'' isliye kuchh wo bhi zikr kiya jisey Taimi ( Moatamir bin Sulaiman ( ne ( ooper wali hadees mein) bayan kiya hai."
1542,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) unhen ye dua is tarah sikhatey they jaisey ke Quran : (اللَّهُمَّ ! إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ عَذَابِ جَهَنَّمَ وَ أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ عَذَابِ الْقَبْرِ وَ أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ فِتْنَةِ الْمَسِيحِ الدَّجَّالِ ، وَأَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ فِتْنَةِ الْمَحْيَا و َالْمَمَاتِ) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun jahannam ke azab sey, qabr ke azab sey, Masih dajjaal ke fitney se aur zindagi aur maut ke fitney se.''"
1543,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) in kalimaat se dua farmaya kartey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ ! إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ فِتْنَةِ النَّارِ وَ عَذَابِ النَّارِ وَمِنْ شَرِّ الْغِنَى وَالْفَقْرِ ) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun aag ke fitney se aur aag ke azab sey, maaldari ke shar se aur faqeeri ke shar se.''"
1544,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye dua farmaya kartey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ الْفَقْرِ وَالْقِلَّةِ وَالذِّلَّةِ , وَأَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ أَنْ أَظْلِمَ أَوْ أُظْلَمَ ) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun mohtaji sey, qillat se aur zillat sey, aur teri panah chahta hun is baat se ke main zulm ka irtikab karun ya mujh par zulm kiya jaey.''"
1545,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki duaon mein se ye dua thi : (اللهم إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ زَوَالِ نِعْمَتِكَ وَتَحْوِيلِ عَافِيَتِكَ وَفُجَاءَةِ نَقْمَتِكَ وَ جَمِيعِ سُخْطِكَ) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun is baat se ke teri koi nemat chhin jaey ya teri di hui tandurusti aur rahat palat jaey ya koi naa-gahaani azab aa jaey. aur terey tamam ghussay aur naraziyon se teri panah chahta hun.''
1546,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye dua farmaya kartey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ ! إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ الشِّقَاقِ وَالنِّفَاقِ وَسُوءِ الْأَخْلَاقِ ) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun is baat se ke) haq ki) mukhalifat karun ya munafiq aur bad akhlaq banoon.''
1547,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye dua farmaya kartey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ ! إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ الْجُوعِ فَإِنَّهُ بِئْسَ الضَّجِيعُ , وَأَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ الْخِيَانَةِ فَإِنَّهَا بِئْسَتِ الْبِطَانَةُ ) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun bhook sey, beshak ye bahut buri ham khuwab hai. aur main teri panah chahta hun khayanat sey, beshak poshida khaslaton mein se ye bahut buri khaslat hai.''"
1548,"Ibaad bin Abi Saeed se marwi (bayan) hai ke unhoney Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye dua kiya kartey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي ! أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ الْأَرْبَعِ : مِنْ عِلْمٍ لَا يَنْفَعُ , وَمِنْ قَلْبٍ لَا يَخْشَعُ , وَمِنْ نَفْسٍ لَا تَشْبَعُ , وَمِنْ دُعَاءٍ لَا يُسْمَعُ ) ''aey Allah ! main chaar chizon se teri panah chahta hun : aisa ilm jo faeyda na dey , aisa dil jis mein khushu na ho, ( terey samney jhuktaa na ho) aisi tabiat jo sair na hoti ho aur aisi dua jo qubul na ho.''"
1549,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye dua kiya kartey they : (اللَّهُمَّ ! إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ صَلَاةٍ لَا تَنْفَعُ) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun aisi Namaz se jo faayda na dey.''  aur eik dusri dua bhi zikr ki.
1550,Farwa bin Nofal Ash'jai kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Aaysha ummul-momenin (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kya dua manga kartey they? unhoney kaha : aap farmaya kartey they : (اللهم ! إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ شَرِّ ما عَمِلْتُ وَمِنْ شَرِّ ما لَمْ أَعْمَلْ) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun un aamaal ke shar se jo maine kiye hain aur un aamaal ke shar se bhi jo maine nahin kiye.''
1551,"Shateer bin Shakl ( Abu-Ahmad yani Muhammad bin Abdullah bin Zuber ki sanad mein us raawi ka naam Shakl bin Humaid hai) apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, wo kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey koi dua sikha dijiye . aapney farmaya ye kaho : ( اللَّهُمَّ ! إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ شَرِّ سَمْعِي وَمِنْ شَرِّ بَصَرِي , وَمِنْ شَرِّ لِسَانِي وَمِنْ شَرِّ قَلْبِي وَمِنْ شَرِّ مَنِيِّي ) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun apney kaan ki burai sey, aankh ki burai sey, zaban ki burai sey, dil ki burai se aur mada manwiya ki burai (ghair aurat ke sath bure kaam karne) se.''"
1552,"Hazrat Abul Yasr (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye dua farmaya kartey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ ! إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنَ الْهَدْمِ , وَأَعُوذُبِكَ مِنَ التَّرَدِّي , وَأَعُوذُبِكَ مِنَ الْغَرَقِ , وَالْحَرَقِ , وَالْهَرَمِ , وَأَعُوذُبِكَ man أَنْ يَتَخَبَّطَنِي الشَّيْطَانُ عِنْدَ الْمَوْتِ وَأَعُوذُبِكَ أَنْ أَمُوتَ فِي سَبِيلِكَ مُدْبِرًا , وَأَعُوذُبِكَ أَنْ أَمُوتَ لَدِيغًا ) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun ke koi makaan ya deewar mujh par aa girey ya kisi buland maqam se gir padoon . main teri panah chahta hun gharq honey sey, jalney ya az-had boodha ho janey se. teri panah chahta hun us se ke shaitan mujhey maut ke waqt bad-hawas kar dey , ya is baat se ke jihad mein peeth detey huey marun ya us kaiyfiyat se ke zahreeley janwer ke kaatey se mujhey maut aaye.''"
1553,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ke maula , Hazrat Abul Yasr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey hain. ... is riwayat mein) والغم (ka izafa bhi hai."
1554,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ye dua farmaya kartey they : ( اللَّهُمَّ ! إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ الْبَرَصِ وَالْجُنُونِ وَالْجُذَامِ وَمِنْ سَيِّئْ الْأَسْقَامِ ) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun baras (phalbhari/safed kodh) sey, pagal pan sey, kodh se aur buri bimariyon se .''"
1555,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik roz masjid mein tashrif laye to kya dekhtey hain ke eik Ansari aadmi hai jis ka naam Abu-Umama tha, aapney farmaya : ''aey Abu-Umama ! kya baat hai ke main tumhen masjid mein dekh raha hun aur Namaz ka waqt bhi nahin hai? ''unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey ghamon aur qarzon ne gher rakha hai, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya main tumhen aisey kalimaat na sikha dun, agar tum unhen padhney lago , tu Allah taala tumharey gham door kar dega aur tumharey qarzey ada kar dega.'' (ada kerney ka sabab paida farma dega.) maine kaha : kyon nahin aey Allah ke Rasool ! farmaya : ''subh aur shaam ye kalimaat padha karo : (اللَّهُمَّ ! إِنِّي أَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ الْهَمِّ وَالْحَزَنِ , وَأَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ الْعَجْزِ وَالْكَسَلِ , وَأَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ الْجُبْنِ وَالْبُخْلِ وَأَعُوذُبِكَ مِنْ غَلَبَةِ الدَّيْنِ وَقَهْرِ الرِّجَالِ ) ''aey Allah ! main teri panah chahta hun pareshani aur gham sey, aajiz reh janey aur kasl mandi se aur teri panah chahta hun buzdili aur bakheeli se aur teri panah chahta hun qarzey aur zalimon ke ghalbey se '' Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine ye dua kerni shuru ki tu Allah taala ne meri pareshaaniyaan door kar dien aur qarzon (ki adaegi) ka sabab bhi paida farma diya."
